sources.title: Fang (Prairie Dog) | Full Movie Adventure Drama
sources.description:
***This film is under license from ITN Distribution. All rights reserved.***

Fang (Prairie Dog) - A lone sheriff of the vast lands and valleys of Brada County is confronted with a dual mystery. A pair of sociopathic criminals being chased across the plains have disappeared, and reports keep surfacing of a large, shadowed animal roaming the farmlands of the county. With the assistance of an environmental consultant and the mayor of the nearby town of Sombra Hollow, the sheriff races to find the connection between the mysteries that haunt the valleys of Brada County.

2015
Stars: John W. Bowers, Sebastian David, Tighe Gill
